1. Diretório: C:\Softwares\Java Script\Projetos\exercicios-web\react\crud\backend>
2. Executar comando: npm init -y (Cria o package.json)
3. Instalar depenência: npm i --save json-server@0.13.0 -E (node_modules) e (package-lock.json)
4. Inserir o script no package.json: "start": "json-server --watch db.json --port 3001"
5. C:\Softwares\Java Script\Projetos\exercicios-web\react\crud\backend>npm start
6. C:\Softwares\Java Script\Projetos\exercicios-web\react\crud> create-react-app frontend
7. (frontend) - package.json:
    "axios": "0.18.0", (cliente http)
    "bootstrap": "4.1.1", (Estilização)
    "font-awesome": "4.7.0",  (Fontes)
    "react-router": "4.2.0", (Para navegar entre os componentes)
    "react-router-dom": "4.2.2",
8. Instalar as depenências:
    C:\Softwares\Java Script\Projetos\exercicios-web\react\crud\frontend> npm i

9. Em frontend >> public >> index.html, inserir o link:
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:300,400,500,700" rel="stylesheet">